de.cesr.more.measures
Interface MoreMeasureCategory

All Known Implementing Classes:
MNetworkMeasureCategory, MNodeMeasureCategory
public interface MoreMeasureCategory

MORe A marker Interface for MAbstractNetworkMeasure categories MoreMeasureCategorys categorize MoreMeasures and are provided by the MoreMeasureSuppliers when these support that category. The MoreNodeMeasureManager and MoreNetworkMeasureManager provide common categories as constants which should be used by custom implementations.

Sascha Holzhauer
